text: Grand Canary is a 1934 American drama movie directed by Irving Cummings and based on the novel of the same name by A. J. Cronin and stars Warner Baxter, Madge Evans, Marjorie Rambeau, Zita Johann, Roger Imhof, Gilbert Emery. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1934 drama movies Category:1930s American drama movies Category:Movies based on books Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Irving Cummings
